Repeat: sl 1 wyib, sl 1 wyif, sl 1 wyib, k1
knit, dropping all yarn overs off needle to make long loose Color B strands across the front of work
sl 1 wyib, insert needle from front under the loose Color B strand and knit the next stitch, bringing the needle out under the strand to catch strand behind stitch; sl 1 wyib, k1
sl 1 wyif, p1, sl 1 wyif, k1
sl 1 wyib, sl 1 wyif, sl 1 wyib, k1
knit, dropping all yarn overs off needle to make long loose Color A strands across the front of work
sl 1 wyib, insert needle from front under the loose Color A strand and knit the next stitch, bringing the needle out under the strand to catch strand behind stitch; sl 1 wyib, k1
sl 1 wyif, p1, sl 1 wyif, k1
